TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {22469=My ranch lies near Coalinga, Ca.  Up until this year... or perhaps mid 2010, wild pigs were out of control.  We couldn't go to my ranch without seeing them.  A friend over a ridge near Priest Valley had the same issue on his ranch.  So many that 'damage' was becoming a major problem.  , 55941=© 2000-2013 Outdoor Hub, LLC, 42255=Huh, interesting for sure.  I know that on Tejon, they jsut had a great December hunt, with about a 50% success rate for 100 hunters.  Sounds like they are still seeing some good numbers down there.  Hopefully that will continue into the next hunt they have.}
